# Beehiiv Integration Rules
When implementing or modifying email subscriptions, always follow the standards in `BEEHIIV_CURSOR_RULES.md`.

- Endpoint: Always use `https://api.beehiiv.com/v2/publications/{publication_id}/subscriptions`.
- Body: Always include `form_id` and `automation_ids`.
- Runtime: Prefer Vercel Edge for speed.
- Error Handling: Always read response as text before parsing JSON.

